    "summary": "Arno Akkermans is professor of law at Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam. On the basis of his expertise in liability and compensation law, he conducts collaborative interdisciplinary and empirical research with others into the experiences and predicaments of those who have to resort to the legal system in general, and in particular to restorative justice for victims not only of crimes, but also of traffic and workplace accidents, medical errors and other causes of harm and injury.  \n\nSpecialties: Tort law, personal injury, empirical legal studies, law and psychology, apology and law, restorative justice, procedural justice, therapeutic jurisprudence, health law, civil procedure, out of court settlement.",
